# .assetsignore — Cloudflare Workers static-assets ignore list (gitignore-
# style syntax). Lives here under public/, NOT at the repo root, because
# Cloudflare only reads `.assetsignore` from INSIDE the configured [assets]
# directory (wrangler.toml points at ./dist, a Vite build output) — same
# constraint netrunner/mail's migrations verified against Cloudflare's
# docs. Vite copies everything under public/ verbatim into dist/, so this
# file lands at dist/.assetsignore on every `npm run build`.
#
# In practice a real `npm run build` (verified during this migration)
# already produces a clean dist/ — no node_modules/.git/docs/source files
# end up there regardless of this list (Vite's build step is the actual
# filter; every game asset is a real ES import, not a copied directory).
# Kept anyway for consistency with the portfolio's canonical set
# (clint-engine/templates/assetsignore) and as a backstop against stray
# .DS_Store files under public/ getting copied verbatim.

**/.wrangler
**/node_modules
**/.git
**/.DS_Store
**/.env
.claude
*.zip
*.md
wrangler.toml
.assetsignore
docs/
